            <p>Wadi El-Gedid dates are among the finest traditional Egyptian dates, with a cultivation history in Egypt that spans hundreds of thousands of years. These dates are known for their exceptional quality and taste, as well as their competitive price. We cultivate them in the Wadi El-Gedid region in southern Egypt, where they thrive in the high temperatures.</p>
