            <h2>Medjool Dates</h2>
            <div class="price"></div>
            <p>This type of date is considered one of the best in the world. It has been recently cultivated in Egypt and has proven to be highly efficient. Medjool dates are among our finest products, rich in fiber and antioxidants that help combat diseases. They may enhance brain health and normal function, serve as an excellent natural sweetener, promote bone health, and assist in blood sugar control.

            Medjool dates have also been able to strongly compete in the global market against traditional growers of this type of date, thanks to their similar qualities and lower price.

            As for the sizes:

                1.	Super Jumbo
                2.	Jumbo
                3.	Large</p>
